name: 結華
text:
お疲れーまみみん
収録無事終わって良かったねぇ
trans:
Good work out there, Mamimin!
I'm glad the recording went well.

name: 摩美々
text: 三峰もお疲れー
trans: Same to you, Mitsumine.

name: 結華
text:
やっぱり私服は楽でいいよ
こういうお仕事、またあるといいな
trans:
It was smooth sailing wearing our own clothes.
I hope we get another job like this.

name: 摩美々
text:
そーかもー
私も悪くなかったと思うー
trans:
I hope sooo...
I didn't think it was a bad time.

name: 摩美々
text:
あとはねー、
私はぁ、衣装合わせが楽しかったなぁ
trans:
Annnd of course...
I had fun trying out new outfits with you.

name: 結華
text: この前の時も、また服見せてって言ってたもんね
trans:
You asked me if I can show you more of my clothes
the other day, didn't you?

name: 摩美々
text:
言ったねー
けっこー好きな感じの服多かったし、また見たいからぁ
trans:
I suuure did. I liked a lot of what I saw,
so I want to see them again.

name: 結華
text:
三峰もまた、まみみんの服みたいよ～
次、まみみんと会えるのはー……
trans:
Mitsumine wants to see Mamimin's clothes again too~
Let's see... The next time we can meet up is...

name: 結華
text:
あっ、この日とか？　レッスンの時間被ってるし
なんか持ってきちゃう？
trans:
Ah. How about on the day our lessons overlap?
I wonder what I should bring this time...

name: 摩美々
text:
じゃあ、その日にしよー
私も服持ってくるからぁ
trans:
Let's do it on that day, theeen.
I'll bring in more of my clothes too.

name: 結華
text:
やっりぃ！
まみみんの服、楽しみにしてるからね！
trans:
Awesome!
I'm looking forward to them!

name: 摩美々
text:
私も三峰の持ってくる服に期待しとこー
ふふー
trans:
I can't wait to see what sort of clothes you'll be
bringing next time, Mitsumine. Fufu...

name: 摩美々
text:
（私もどれを持っていくか考えよー
家にある服で三峰に似合いそうなのはぁ……）
trans:
(Now to figure out what to bring. I wonder what I
have back home that would look good on Mitsumine...)

name: 摩美々
text:
（あ、そーいえばあの服まだ見せてなかったっけー？
三峰好きそーだしあれ持っていこうかなぁ……）
trans:
(Oh right. I didn't show her that one outfit yet, did I?
It seems like something Mitsumine would like,
so I should bring that one over...)

name: 摩美々
text:
おはよーございまぁす
あー、三峰もう来てたんだぁ？
trans:
Gooood moooorning...
Ahhh... You're alreaady here, Mitsumine?

name: 結華
text:
おはよーまみみん！　そりゃあ楽しみだったからねぇ
それより見て見てこれっ！
trans:
Goood morning, Mamimin! That's because I was
excited! Check these out!

name: 摩美々
text: ……あれー？　この服見たことないやつだよねー？
trans: What the... Aren't these waaay different from before?

name: 結華
text:
さっすがお目が高い！
今日のはね、こないだ持ってきた服とは全部違うやつだよ
trans:
Good eyes you have there!
Indeed, today's clothes are different!

name: 結華
text:
ほら、これなんてどう？
三峰としてはまみみんにぜひ着てほしいんだけど
trans:
Here, what do you think of this?
Mitsumine would love for Mamimin to try this on.

name: 摩美々
text:
どれー？
……これは、確かにいいかもねー、かわいすぎなくてー
trans:
Which one?
...Oh this one's good. It's not too cute either.

name: 結華
text:
だよねだよね！
あとは～……これとか、あとそれも……
trans:
Exactly! Next up is this one~
And this one too! And maybe this one after...

name: 摩美々
text:
けっこーたくさん見たかもー
三峰たくさん持ってきてたからねー
trans:
Mitsumine, you brought in so many clothes
for me to look at...

name: 結華
text:
三峰としてはこれでもまだ足りないくらいなんだよ？
でもまぁそろそろ、まみみんの服も見たいかなぁ
trans:
Having all of these isn't enough for me, y'know?
But I think it's time for me to see what clothes you
brought in, Mamimin.

name: 摩美々
text:
いいよー好きに見てー
私も三峰にまだ見せてないの持ってきたからぁ
trans:
Go aheaaad. Look all you want.
I got stuff that I haven't shown you yet too.

name: 結華
text: ありがと！　ふっふ～ん♪
trans: Thanks! Huhu~♪

name: 摩美々
text:
あ、そーだ、
あれ先に渡しとこーかなぁ……
trans: Oh right, I should probably hand this over...

name: 摩美々
text:
三峰、ちょっと待ってー
先に渡したいのあるから服見るのストップー
trans:
Hold on, Mitsumine... Stop looking around at my
clothes so I can give this to you.

name: 結華
text:
ん？　いいけど……
渡したいもの？
trans:
Hm? Sure then...
What did you want me to try on?

name: 摩美々
text:
えっとー
これなんだけどー……三峰にあげよーと思ってー
trans:
Well...
I was thinking of actually giving this to you.

name: 摩美々
text:
合わせるの難しいケド
三峰ならだいじょーぶだと思うー
trans:
It's a hard piece to fit into an outfit, but I think you
can figure out something to wear it with.

name: 結華
text:
ありがとう。……でもまたなんで三峰に？
や、くれるんならありがたくもらうんだけども
trans:
Oh thanks, but... why give it to Mitsumine?
Well, I'm glad you're giving it to me but...

name: 結華
text:
わぉ、まみみんこんな服も持ってたんだ
これはこれは、なかなか合わせるのが難しそうな……
trans:
Oh wow, even Mamimin has something like this!
This one really looks like a challenge to match...

name: 摩美々
text:
買ったのはいいんだケドー、
それっきり着てなくてー
trans:
I was happy when buying it,
but I never wore it since.

name: 摩美々
text:
でも、この服三峰っぽいし、
似合いそうだなぁーって思ったんだよねー
trans:
But it pretty much has "Mitsumine" written
all over it. So I think it'll look great on you.

name: 結華
text: 三峰っぽいって、どの辺が？
trans: What about me makes it "Mitsumine?"

name: 摩美々
text: んー、どの辺って言われてもー……
trans: Hmm, what about you, huh?

name: 摩美々
text: 三峰っぽいは、三峰っぽいってことー
trans:
What makes it "Mitsumine" is the
"Mitsumine"-ness it has.

name: 結華
text:
えー？
気になるじゃん、教えて教えて？
trans:
Ehhh? Oh don't leave me hanging like that!
Can't you tell me?

name: 摩美々
text:
そんなこと言われてもー、
私もうまく言えないしー
trans:
Even if you beg like thaaat,
I can't put it well enough in words.

name: 結華
text:
そうなの？
うーん、着てみたら何かわかりそう？
trans:
You sure?
Welp, guess I'll find out when I put it on, then.

name: 摩美々
text:
そーだねー
試しに着てみなよー
trans: That's riiight, juuust try it on.

name: 結華
text:
おっけー。そしたら例えばこれとこれを……
このパンツと合わせて……小物もつけて……
trans:
Okay... Then I can pair it with this one...
Same with these pants here...
This accessory should work with it too...

name: 結華
text:
こんな感じで！
まみみん的にはどう？
trans:
Eureka! I got it!
How does it look, Mamimin?

name: 摩美々
text:
（自己主張強いケド、周りと合わせるのが上手な三峰って
感じのコーディネートだなぁ）
trans:
(Mitsumine may be bold and assertive, but she's also
skilled at fitting in wherever she's at. The outfit she
put together is just like her personality.)

name: 摩美々
text: ……そっかぁー
trans: ...I seee.

name: 結華
text: え。どしたの、何に納得したのさまみみん？
trans: Eh? What's wrong? Does it look good, Mamimin?

name: 摩美々
text: やっぱり三峰っぽいなぁ、って思ってー
trans: Just as I thought. It's very "Mitsumine."

name: 結華
text:
またそれー？
そりゃあ三峰が考えてるんだから三峰っぽいだろうけど
trans:
We're doing this again? Maybe it's "Mitsumine"
because this outfit is Mitsumine's idea.

name: 結華
text: そういう感じで言ってるんじゃないよね？
trans: Was that what you're trying to say?

name: 摩美々
text:
んー……、
やっぱりナイショー
trans:
Heh...
I'm not telling.

name: 結華
text: ええー、教えてよ～！
trans: Ehhhh?! Tell meee~!

name: 摩美々
text: ふふー、だーめー
trans: Fufu, nooot happening.

name: off
text: off
trans: off
